.SH NAME
drm_vblank_work_cancel_sync \- cancel a vblank work and wait for it to finish executing
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "bool" drm_vblank_work_cancel_sync
.BI "(struct drm_vblank_work *work "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "work" 12
vblank work to cancel
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Cancel an already scheduled vblank work and wait for its
execution to finish.

On return, \fIwork\fP is guaranteed to no longer be scheduled or running, even
if it's self-arming.
.SH "RETURN"
True if the work was cancelled before it started to execute, false
otherwise.
